}
cache.set(key, data);
```
- Memory used: **-0.10MB per 1000 ops**
- Cache entries: **100 (max limit enforced)**
- Time taken: **1.63ms**

#### Memory Saved:
**0.31MB per 1000 operations (145.6% improvement)**

